{
  "stem": "11179.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They missed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Japanese radio station was right next to a camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And about-- I think about 60 of refugees got killed in that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can't find [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We talked to the people later on that it's a bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The way-- they explained how it is done, you cannot-- at that time, you couldn't pinpoint bomb.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know you can do it today better, but probably.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But at that time, they-- they told us how that was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a lot of people-- a lot more Chinese got killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had to organize ourselves in air raid groups already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And to be prepared for something like this, even though we-- we hoped not-- that would never happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because before the bombing was usually warehouses and other strategic areas of Shanghai, never the area where we lived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was the only time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nearby, yes, but that was the only time it was really full hits.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I-- we were working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were used to have-- the planes came daytime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Those were the B-24s.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think they flew high enough that the-- the Japanese anti-aircraft couldn't reach them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Whether they were B-24s or B-29s, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were very high and very small.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when it hit there, we went out to the-- we were-- we were about eight or 10 of us all in our late teens-- mid- to late teens, I should say.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And across the street, there was a first aid station in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we got ourselves-- four of us got ourselves a carrier-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You carry-- carry wounded people-- a carrier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we went out and picked up some of the wounded.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
